snippet.title: Arla MilkOut! E-Game (Windows game 200?)
snippet.description:
Arla MilkOut! is a simple Swedish breakout-like puzzle game by E-Game.
After you destroy a brick, a drop of milk falls down.
Some drops of milk have special functions.
